      <div class="swiper-slide">
        <p class="body-paragraph ws-reviews__cards--review">"There are rare persons who, when we meet them, bring light and energy to our lives; persons who show, almost without speaking, their deep commitment to others.  Deo Mwano is such a person.  While his personal story is one of strength gained through adversity, his enthusiasm for youth and its potential and for education and its empowering effect is a message he does not just talk about, but truly lives."</p>
